‚ô•Ô∏èHave high self-esteem and self-respect.
‚ô•Ô∏èShare personal information gradually, in a mutually sharing and trusting relationship.
‚ô•Ô∏èProtect physical and emotional space from intrusion.
‚ô•Ô∏èHave an equal partnership where responsibility and power are shared.
‚ô•Ô∏èBe assertive. Confidently and truthfully say ‚Äúyes‚Äù or ‚Äúno‚Äù and be okay when others say ‚Äúno‚Äù to you.
‚ô•Ô∏èSeparate your needs, thoughts, feelings, and desires from others. ‚ô•Ô∏èRecognize that your boundaries and needs are different from others.
‚ô•Ô∏èEmpower yourself to make healthy choices and take responsibility for yourself.";}i:199;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:200;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:1;}i:201;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvLVTtjb_0";}i:202;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:238:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118770837_341838427013994_2071433772985910422_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_ohc=2kcwKbzpam0AX9cixh0&oh=8368fd1a9cf42f2f1f8aad9884997037&oe=5F7E3E2A";}i:203;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:204;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:11637392472;}i:205;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:206;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:207;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:208;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391179736558069810";}i:209;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvLU0np-gy";}i:210;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599270859;}i:211;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:981:"'JL Keez Anorexia Unlocked' offers an online experience where you are able to explore your eating disorder, or other associated illnesses, within your own time and where ever you choose. There is no fixed timeline - work through the programs at your pace. Learn from the one who has navigated this path before you.
